<TEXT>
<P>
Doctors treating injured motorcycle racer Bubba Shobert at San Jose Medical 
Center said he remains critical but stable, and that they have been able to 
reduce medication required to keep him sedated. Shobert suffered head injuries 
in an accident after the main event of last Sunday's U.S. International Grand 
Prix at Laguna Seca Raceway. 
