EDWARD R; ALATORRE, RICHARD; LOS ANGELES -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; 
BUILDING RESTORATIONS; REMODELING; EAST LOS ANGELES COMMUNITY UNION 
</P>
