ORGANIZATIONS; TAX EXEMPT STATUS; AUDITS; FINANCIAL DISCLOSURE; LOS ANGELES -- 
CONTRACTS; MISUSE OF PUBLIC FUNDS; LOS ANGELES -- TRADE -- AFRICA; LOS ANGELES 
-- FINANCES 
</P>
