LABOR RELATIONS; LOS ANGELES -- SCHOOLS; LOS ANGELES UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT; 
UNITED TEACHERS OF LOS ANGELES; GRADES (EDUCATION); HUNTINGTON PARK HIGH SCHOOL 
</P>
