<P>
SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION; TELEPHONE CALLS; HISPANICS -- UNITED STATES; 
ROYBAL, EDWARD R; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES; CUSTOMER SERVICE; HOT 
LINES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
