<P>
CADHAM, STELLE LEAD AGOURA SWIMMERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Led by Tyler Cadham and Jason Stelle, the Agoura High boys' swim team remained 
undefeated with a 121-33 victory over Santa Clara in a Frontier League meet 
Friday at Agoura. 
</P>
<P>
Cadham won the 500-yard freestyle in 5 minutes, 8.92 seconds and swam legs in 
the victorious 400 freestyle relay (3:37.53) and 200 medley relay (1:53.37). 
</P>
<P>
Stelle, who also swam legs in the relay events, won the 200 freestyle in 
1:57.23 for Agoura (8-0, 4-0 in league meets). 
</P>
<P>
GIRLS' SWIMMING 
</P>
<P>
