<P>
GIRLS' TRACK 
</P>
<P>
Kennedy 84 1/2, Cleveland 7 1/2 -- Daima Calhoun won the long jump with a mark 
of 14 feet, 11 1/2 inches and cleared 4-6 to win the high jump for host Kennedy 
in the North Valley League meet. 
</P>
<P>
The victory clinched the Golden Cougars' 11th consecutive dual-meet league 
crown. Kennedy (7-0) won 10 consecutive Mid-Valley League titles before moving 
to the North Valley League this season. 
</P>
<P>
Kisa Martin won the 300-meter low hurdles in 52.7 for Kennedy. She also placed 
second (17.5) in the 100 low hurdles behind teammate Kathy McClain (17.0). 
