anchored Birmingham's victorious mile-relay team in a Mid-Valley League meet. 
</P>
<P>
Segal won the 880 (2:35.5), mile (5:57.6) and two-mile (13:01.2) as Birmingham 
(8-0, 7-0) clinched the league title. 
</P>
