Birmingham 84, Reseda 42 -- Rodney Burt won three events and anchored the 
Braves' victorious 440-yard relay team in a Mid-Valley League meet at Reseda. 
</P>
<P>
Burt took the 100 meters (11.0), the 220 yards (22.9) and the 440 (51.3) as 
