<P>
ROBBERIES -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042289-0137 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 48263 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 22, 1989, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
