(Ocean View), 6-6, 250; Miguel Ochoa (Saddleback), 6-1, 235; Brian Turk (Mater 
Dei), 6-4, 260; QB -- David Henigan (Fountain Valley), 6-1, 185; David Lowery 
(Trabuco Hills), 6-0, 180; RB -- David Nemeth (El Toro), 5-11, 197; Gary Smarr 
(University), 6-1, 195; Tom Walker (Newport Harbor), 6-2, 195. 
</P>
